189
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:53,780
I'm surprised, I'm surprised.

190
00:12:53,780 --> 00:12:58,770
Your thoughts are scarily too meticulous that you didn't even spare a child.

191
00:12:58,770 --> 00:13:03,690
I'm just afraid that he'll invite unnecessary romance while here in the mortal world.

192
00:13:03,690 --> 00:13:06,460
They all said that Second Sister-in-Law is the most easily jealous in our Bai Family.

193
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:09,670
How come I feel that you're worse than her?

194
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,750
Fourth Older Brother!

195
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,530
Even if I tell you, you wouldn't understand.

196
00:13:13,530 --> 00:13:17,530
In Heaven and Earth, you are the one who least understands women.

197
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:38,000
Young Master, you are awake.

198
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:49,350
Green Hill?

199
00:13:58,990 --> 00:14:01,690
Young Master, what are you looking for?

200
00:14:01,690 --> 00:14:05,280
I'm looking for a place called Green Hill.

201
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:06,780
Green Hill?

202
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:08,560
What a strange name.

203
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:12,650
I've accompanied you in your studies every day and have never heard of it.

204
00:14:12,650 --> 00:14:14,500
Young Master, stop looking.

205
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:16,770
