249
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:38,840
Since you're here, too, why don't you join us for drinks?

250
00:17:38,840 --> 00:17:41,940
Mo Yuan once took some tens of thousand-year-old good brew from my place.

251
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:44,010
Today's the perfect day to drink them.

252
00:17:44,010 --> 00:17:46,620
Sure! Drinking wine can drown my sorrows.

253
00:17:46,620 --> 00:17:49,150
Problems would just get more worrisome.

254
00:17:50,870 --> 00:17:54,750
Then, I will just worry about them tomorrow.

255
00:18:05,810 --> 00:18:08,910
I still remember that when you asked me for this wine,

256
00:18:08,910 --> 00:18:12,170
it was for Young Fifth's birthday present. Right?

257
00:18:12,170 --> 00:18:13,730
Yes.

258
00:18:13,730 --> 00:18:18,540
I also recall that. It's a pity that I didn't even get to drink it

259
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:20,930
before I was caught by Teacher's admirer, High Goddess Yao Guang.

260
00:18:20,930 --> 00:18:22,620
I was imprisoned in the Water Prison.

261
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:24,890
My birthday was spent in the Water Prison.

262
00:18:24,890 --> 00:18:26,930
- It was really unforgettable.
- Oh?

263
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,390
Did that really happen between him and Yao Guang?

264
00:18:29,390 --> 00:18:33,240
Let's not discuss a person who has returned to the formless mass.

265
00:18:36,010 --> 00:18:37,790
I said the wrong thing.

266
00:18:37,790 --> 00:18:39,690
I will punish myself with this cup of wine.

267
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:46,710
Old Phoenix, tell me about the emperor's past.

268
00:18:49,650 --> 00:18:52,130
Dong Hua?

269
00:18:52,130 --> 00:18:56,440
He's even worse than Mo Yuan at getting close to women.

270
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:58,380
Why doesn't he get close to women, either?

271
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:01,250
Is he a man or not?

272
00:19:01,250 --> 00:19:05,270
Young Jiu, you must get this straight.

273
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:09,470
That man in your heart used to be the ruler of Heaven and Earth.

274
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:12,170
He's an outstanding man.

275
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:19,050
In any case, I also respect you for choosing such a person from thousands of others.

276
00:19:19,050 --> 00:19:22,040
You are not allowed to talk bad about him.

277
00:19:23,010 --> 00:19:27,570
This little brat's alcohol tolerance is nothing compared to yours.

278
00:19:27,570 --> 00:19:29,080
It's good to have bad alcohol tolerance.

279
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:30,790
You will get drunk faster.

280
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:36,720
But Zhe Yan, do you know why this Emperor Dong Hua doesn't get close to women?

281
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:39,340
It's because of Four Seas and Eight Wildernesses.

282
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:47,560
Yes, it's because of the Four Seas and Eight Wildernesses.

283
00:20:09,710 --> 00:20:14,310
When I came with Zhe Yan a few days ago, I could still go up the mountain freely.

284
00:20:14,310 --> 00:20:19,340
With the dragon aura here now, I feel that it's hard to approach it.

285
00:20:20,850 --> 00:20:26,070
So to say, High God Mo Yuan's spirit has returned to his body.

286
00:20:36,770 --> 00:20:39,510
Brothers, why are you standing here?

287
00:20:40,410 --> 00:20:42,030
It's nothing.

288
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:46,190
I only feel that Kunlun Void has restored its life again,

289
00:20:46,190 --> 00:20:48,330
so I'm here to take a look.

290
00:20:48,330 --> 00:20:50,650
High God Mo Yuan's spirit has returned to his body.

291
00:20:50,650 --> 00:20:56,450
Even High God Zhe Yan, High God Bai Zhen of Green Hill, and the Great Lady are here.

292
00:20:58,180 --> 00:21:00,420
I see.

293
00:21:02,570 --> 00:21:04,620
Thank you for letting me know.

294
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:12,660
This man is strange.

295
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:17,000
After hearing that High God Mo Yuan is back, he doesn't look happy.

296
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:20,900
Could he be from another tribe?

297
00:21:20,900 --> 00:21:22,810
Probably so.

298
00:21:34,250 --> 00:21:35,740
Young Jiu.

299
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:37,730
Aunt, morning.

300
00:21:37,730 --> 00:21:41,810
It's not morning anymore. Fourth Older Brother and the others have been waiting for you for a long time.

301
00:21:41,810 --> 00:21:44,650
- They are waiting for me?
- That's right.

302
00:21:44,650 --> 00:21:49,370
You should know that the Heavenly Tribe and Green Hill are preparing to hold the wedding between me and Ye Hua.

303
00:21:49,370 --> 00:21:50,920
You are going to take over my post.

304
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:54,370
You should concentrate on more serious matters and go back to Green Hill soon.

305
00:21:55,270 --> 00:21:59,100
Aunt, you want me to go back and take over your post?

306
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:03,340
In Green Hill, you're the only girl of your generation.

307
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:05,610
If you don't accept it, who would?

308
00:22:06,370 --> 00:22:09,420
You want me to give up on Dong Hua, too.

309
00:22:10,150 --> 00:22:12,760
I didn't say that.

310
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:17,680
If you marry into the Heavenly Tribe, you can't succeed the throne.

311
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:22,210
Because you are marrying into the Heavenly Palace, you won't be able to take care of the people in Green Hill.

312
00:22:22,210 --> 00:22:26,660
But if I want to marry Emperor Dong Hua, I will marry into the Heavenly Palace, too.

313
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:29,800
I won't be able to take care of the people in Green Hill, either.

314
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:32,020
Aunt, you obviously knew about this.

315
00:22:32,020 --> 00:22:34,850
Why do you still want me to take the throne?

316
00:22:34,850 --> 00:22:38,600
Aunt, do you want me to remain forever in Green Hill?

317
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:43,760
Young Jiu,

318
00:22:43,760 --> 00:22:46,000
just forget him.

319
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:51,820
But, Aunt, you told me last night that you can't forget Crown Prince Ye Hua, either,

320
00:22:51,820 --> 00:22:54,170
because you like him.

321
00:22:54,170 --> 00:22:59,170
What you can't do, why do you want me to handle it instead?

322
00:23:07,150 --> 00:23:10,840
Young Jiu, listen to me.

323
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:14,660
You are not fated to be with Dong Hua.

324
00:23:14,660 --> 00:23:17,010
Why must you force it?

325
00:23:18,820 --> 00:23:23,620
I thought that you were on my side last night,

326
00:23:23,620 --> 00:23:27,460
that even if everyone in our family wanted to lock me up,

327
00:23:27,460 --> 00:23:30,250
you were the only one who could free me,

328
00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:35,840
that you would let me try to make the emperor fall in love with me again.

329
00:23:40,370 --> 00:23:43,310
I don't want to be the monarchess.

330
00:23:43,310 --> 00:23:47,470
If I become the monarchess, I won't be able to go to Nine Heavens again!

331
00:23:47,470 --> 00:23:49,200
Young Jiu!

332
00:23:53,590 --> 00:23:55,430
Young Jiu!

333
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:58,670
Young Jiu!

334
00:23:59,870 --> 00:24:01,960
It still doesn't work?

335
00:24:03,060 --> 00:24:06,630
I merely told her to go back to Green Hill and take over the post of the monarchess,

336
00:24:06,630 --> 00:24:08,960
and she started crying like this.

337
00:24:09,890 --> 00:24:14,170
Between the both of you, one was enlightened too early and other too late.

338
00:24:14,170 --> 00:24:15,790
Forget about this. Leave this to me.

339
00:24:15,790 --> 00:24:18,110
I will escort her home safely.

340
00:24:19,110 --> 00:24:22,570
Tell Second Older Brother not to pressure her too much.

341
00:24:22,570 --> 00:24:25,840
Don't worry. I know what I'm doing.

342
00:24:25,840 --> 00:24:28,510
You are her aunt, and you dote on her.

343
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:32,490
I'm her fourth uncle who equally dotes on her.

344
00:24:32,490 --> 00:24:36,520
Zhe Yan is worried about Mo Yuan's health and needs to remain in Kunlun Void for a few more days.

345
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:38,030
I will leave first.

346
00:24:38,030 --> 00:24:39,910
All right.

347
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:55,630
Do you want to see Ah Yin?

348
00:24:55,630 --> 00:24:57,820
I do.

349
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:02,000
Me, too.

350
00:25:02,970 --> 00:25:08,280
Perhaps, this is the last chance for me to see her.

351
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:11,530
Isn't His Highness the Crown Prince marrying her soon?

352
00:25:11,530 --> 00:25:14,600
By then, the wedding invitation will be delivered to the Grand Purple Palace.

353
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:17,360
You will be able to see them.

354
00:25:27,740 --> 00:25:29,510
I can't wait that long.

355
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:31,430
You can't wait that long?

356
00:25:31,430 --> 00:25:33,610
Why not?

357
00:25:33,610 --> 00:25:36,330
Isn't it soon?

358
00:25:53,890 --> 00:25:56,810
What are you looking at?

359
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:02,640
Little girl, you are ugly when you cry.

360
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:05,750
It's a rare sight in Kunlun Void.

361
00:26:06,700 --> 00:26:09,810
You said that I look ugly when I cry?

362
00:26:09,810 --> 00:26:14,560
Then, I will stay here and cry till you can't take it anymore.

363
00:26:16,990 --> 00:26:18,890
Cry then.

364
00:26:18,890 --> 00:26:20,960
You are only making it hard for yourself.

365
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:23,310
It doesn't concern me.

366
00:26:35,850 --> 00:26:38,860
Does this cave look nice?

367
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:43,550
To me, it's very nice.

368
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:49,210
Such an uninteresting person.

369
00:26:49,210 --> 00:26:51,540
That's right.

370
00:26:51,540 --> 00:26:53,560
Uninteresting.

371
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:57,040
I said that you are an uninteresting person.

372
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:59,460
I know.

373
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:02,210
I was talking about myself, too.

374
00:27:02,210 --> 00:27:07,900
Standing in front of the cave and looking back past tens of thousands of years ago,

375
00:27:07,900 --> 00:27:14,280
I just realized that my life is endless and uninteresting.

376
00:27:31,470 --> 00:27:33,710
- Good boy.
- Winged Monarch.

377
00:27:36,770 --> 00:27:40,280
Second Older Brother, did you meet His Highness the Crown Prince?

378
00:27:40,280 --> 00:27:42,110
No.

379
00:27:42,110 --> 00:27:43,610
You didn't?

380
00:27:43,610 --> 00:27:47,940
Did you meet Heavenly Monarch or Emperor Dong Hua then?

381
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:51,530
Why not?

382
00:27:51,530 --> 00:27:57,250
Aren't you afraid that Father will break out from Donghuang Bell and use Red Lotus Fire to destroy the Four Seas?

383
00:27:57,250 --> 00:28:00,180
And that's why you went to Heavenly Tribe to discuss this?

384
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:03,850
The Winged Realm is in great chaos now.

385
00:28:03,850 --> 00:28:07,600
Many sub-tribe chieftains are currently unable to suppress the mobs.

386
00:28:07,600 --> 00:28:10,560
Second Older Brother, we can't delay any further.

387
00:28:10,560 --> 00:28:12,800
If Father really breaks out from the Donghuang Bell,

388
00:28:12,800 --> 00:28:15,640
many people will follow him.

389
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:19,440
By then, when we go to the Heavenly Tribe to plead, it will be too late.

390
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:21,490
I know.

391
00:28:21,490 --> 00:28:23,240
Second Older Brother!

392
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:26,660
Say something. Let me know what's on your mind.

393
00:28:26,660 --> 00:28:29,300
Or else, I'll die from anxiety.

394
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:35,480
Yan Zhi, do you know?

395
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:38,310
Ah Yin and the Crown Prince will marry soon.

396
00:28:38,310 --> 00:28:40,950
They were previously engaged.

397
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:46,840
This is a marital alliance between the Heavenly Tribe and Green Hill.

398
00:28:46,840 --> 00:28:51,190
This is the most prestigious marriage in Four Seas.

399
00:28:58,660 --> 00:29:04,260
In the past, I thought that, as a prince of the Winged Tribe,

400
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:07,580
I would give my most beloved woman the best wedding.

401
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:11,850
But compared to Ye Hua,

402
00:29:11,850 --> 00:29:14,500
that's such a joke.

403
00:29:16,140 --> 00:29:18,280
Second Older Brother,

404
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:21,360
I know you only have High Goddess Bai Qian in your heart.

405
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:23,410
But...

406
00:29:26,980 --> 00:29:30,360
High God Mo Yuan's spirit is back to his body now,

407
00:29:32,850 --> 00:29:35,260
and Ah Yin is in Kunlun Void.

408
00:29:35,260 --> 00:29:37,990
She must be extremely happy.

409
00:29:37,990 --> 00:29:41,030
High God Mo Yuan's spirit is back to his body?!

410
00:29:41,940 --> 00:29:46,680
That's good. Second Older Brother, let's go and tell High God Mo Yuan.

411
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:51,230
That our lives are the key to helping Father increase his power.

412
00:29:51,230 --> 00:29:57,780
Tell Kunlun Void that because Eldest Brother died, Father is already stronger,

413
00:29:57,780 --> 00:30:00,460
so he can't remain sealed.

414
00:30:00,460 --> 00:30:02,080
We can't tell them.

415
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:04,710
Why?

416
00:30:04,710 --> 00:30:07,540
Yan Zhi, have you ever thought of this?

417
00:30:07,540 --> 00:30:11,510
If Father breaks out from Donghuang Bell, who will seal him?

418
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:14,810
Of course, it's High God Mo Yuan.

419
00:30:14,810 --> 00:30:18,120
Donghuang Bell was created by him.

420
00:30:18,120 --> 00:30:21,570
70,000 years ago, he succeeded once in sealing Father.

421
00:30:21,570 --> 00:30:24,160
Naturally, it will be him again.

422
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:26,200
Think carefully again.

423
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:29,370
If Ah Yin finds out that Mo Yuan wants to seal him,

424
00:30:29,370 --> 00:30:33,060
would she let her Teacher disperse his soul again?

425
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:39,840
By then, she will definitely go all out to protect her teacher.

426
00:30:41,950 --> 00:30:44,540
Seeing that she's going to marry soon,

427
00:30:45,800 --> 00:30:50,350
I don't want anything to happen to her at this time.

428
00:30:50,350 --> 00:30:52,130
But...

429
00:30:55,430 --> 00:30:58,030
As the Winged Monarch for 70,000 years,

430
00:30:58,840 --> 00:31:03,120
I never did any good deed to bring blessings to my citizens and the Winged Realm.

431
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:10,130
I was wandering around the Mortal World looking for the whereabouts of Ah Yin.

432
00:31:10,740 --> 00:31:13,710
As of today,

433
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:17,050
if I still don't do anything,

434
00:31:17,050 --> 00:31:20,260
I will be incompetent trash.

435
00:31:20,260 --> 00:31:22,210
Second Older Brother, you...

436
00:31:22,760 --> 00:31:24,780
What are you talking about?

437
00:31:55,060 --> 00:31:56,890
Second Older Brother, what are you doing?

438
00:31:56,890 --> 00:31:59,060
Get up now.

439
00:32:06,890 --> 00:32:08,710
Yan Zhi,

440
00:32:10,050 --> 00:32:13,060
I'm entrusting my son to you.

441
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:16,550
In the Grand Purple Palace,

442
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:19,560
you will be the only one left with royal blood.

443
00:32:20,910 --> 00:32:26,350
I'm even entrusting the Winged Realm to you today.

444
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:28,850
Second Older Brother, what are you going to do?

445
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:42,150
- Fire Kirin.
- Mighty Monarch.

446
00:32:52,080 --> 00:32:54,770
Lock up the princess in Land of Extreme Coldness.

447
00:32:54,770 --> 00:32:59,180
Before the issue of Donghuang Bell is concluded, don't let her out.

448
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:01,610
No, I can't leave you.

449
00:33:01,610 --> 00:33:03,160
Listen to me!

450
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:05,580
I can't.

451
00:33:05,580 --> 00:33:08,880
Even you don't want to acknowledge me as your monarch?

452
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:12,540
It's not that.

453
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:17,830
You grew up with me.

454
00:33:17,830 --> 00:33:22,720
Other than my mother, you are my closest family.

455
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:28,890
I can only hand over Yan Zhi and the child to you so that I can be at ease.

456
00:33:28,890 --> 00:33:30,800
Do you understand?

457
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:38,920
Mighty Monarch, can I find you again after I have escorted the princess there?

458
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:43,090
You can't.

459
00:33:43,780 --> 00:33:49,070
When I'm dead, I want you to help Yan Zhi become the new Winged Monarchess.

460
00:33:49,970 --> 00:33:53,050
You are the most auspicious deity beast in the Winged Realm.

461
00:33:53,050 --> 00:33:58,350
With you by Yan Zhi's side, no one will dare to hurt Yan Zhi.

462
00:33:58,350 --> 00:34:05,690
Without Father, without me, they will naturally acknowledge Yan Zhi as the Winged Monarchess.

463
00:34:08,530 --> 00:34:10,840
Hurry and take the princess away!

464
00:34:12,460 --> 00:34:14,400
- Yes!
- Yes!

465
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:30,920
- Mighty Monarch...
- Leave!

466
00:34:53,730 --> 00:34:55,650
Seven days.

467
00:34:56,660 --> 00:34:59,390
Give me seven days.

468
00:34:59,390 --> 00:35:02,260
I will definitely succeed.

469
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:17,560
For the past few days, there has been great waves in Ruoshui.

470
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:20,610
I wonder what the reason is.

471
00:35:20,610 --> 00:35:22,770
It doesn't seem that simple.

472
00:35:22,770 --> 00:35:25,630
We must be careful and take precautions.

473
00:35:44,220 --> 00:35:46,210
A guest is here to pay homage again.

474
00:35:46,210 --> 00:35:48,510
Brew tea.

475
00:35:50,350 --> 00:35:54,550
Zhe Yan, stop fooling around. Let me sleep.

476
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:57,550
I didn't have a good rest yesterday.

477
00:35:58,350 --> 00:36:01,920
I'm here to find you regarding an important matter.

478
00:36:03,950 --> 00:36:07,600
What important matter would you have for coming to Kunlun Void?

479
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:13,970
High God Mo Yuan has already set the date for his seclusion.

480
00:36:13,970 --> 00:36:16,330
It's in seven days.

481
00:36:16,330 --> 00:36:18,670
I'm going to refine some medicinal pills for him

482
00:36:18,670 --> 00:36:22,790
to take into seclusion at the cave to help him with his recovery.

483
00:36:22,790 --> 00:36:26,210
During this period, I want you to assist me.

484
00:36:26,210 --> 00:36:28,490
Teacher is going into seclusion?

485
00:36:28,490 --> 00:36:31,750
He has been back for eleven days. He should go into seclusion.

486
00:36:31,750 --> 00:36:35,620
After all, the cultivation of Ye Hua was only enough to wake him up.

487
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:40,230
He's still very weak, and needs to rest and recuperate.

488
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:48,600
For the past days, you were either at the pharmacy or the Pellet-Cultivating Furnace.

489
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:53,740
You didn't even have time to drink some tea and moisten your throat.

490
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:56,830
If you have nothing to do today, go visit your teacher.

491
00:36:56,830 --> 00:37:01,110
I fear when he goes into seclusion, you won't be able to see him for quite a while.

492
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:04,720
How long will Teacher be in seclusion?

493
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:08,920
It could be 10 days, or half a month, or even 10 years.

494
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:12,430
I'll go see Teacher right now.

495
00:37:14,110 --> 00:37:17,990
Oh! Teacher loves peach blossoms.

496
00:37:17,990 --> 00:37:22,380
I'm going to pick some to replace the ones in Teacher's room.

497
00:37:49,290 --> 00:37:51,330
I love hearing you play the zither.

498
00:37:51,330 --> 00:37:54,550
It always soothes me.

499
00:37:54,550 --> 00:37:59,640
Can I become a high immortal faster if I listen to you play more often?

500
00:38:10,850 --> 00:38:16,520
Teacher, I'm going to help Zhe Yan refine your medical pills tomorrow.

501
00:38:16,520 --> 00:38:19,440
I won't be able to greet you for many days.

502
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:23,440
I'm here especially to replace your peach blossoms.

503
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,780
Peach blossoms wither after just one day.

504
00:38:25,780 --> 00:38:30,910
I've instructed Sixteenth Senior to come and change them every day from now on.

505
00:38:33,060 --> 00:38:37,030
You came just for that tonight?

506
00:38:40,190 --> 00:38:43,360
Teacher, ever since you came back to Kunlun Void,

507
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:47,810
we have been very busy, so I haven't had time to have a proper chat with you.

508
00:38:47,810 --> 00:38:52,490
Moreover, Zhe Yan told me that you are going into seclusion soon.

509
00:38:52,490 --> 00:38:56,770
It could take ten days, half a month, or even several years,

510
00:38:56,770 --> 00:39:00,440
so I wanted to come see you.

511
00:39:06,830 --> 00:39:09,570
Am I bothering you?

512
00:39:09,570 --> 00:39:11,530
No.

513
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:17,340
I remember when I first came to Kunlun Void, I was very childish.

514
00:39:17,340 --> 00:39:20,020
I only knew that you played the zither very well,

515
00:39:20,020 --> 00:39:22,880
so I bugged you to play musical pieces every day.

516
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:25,070
Do you remember?

517
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,470
I remember.

518
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:33,870
Speaking of which, I've never heard Ye Hua play for me.

519
00:39:38,690 --> 00:39:42,850
Does Ye Hua... treat you well?

520
00:39:44,050 --> 00:39:48,600
His way of treating me well is different from the way you treat me well.

521
00:39:48,600 --> 00:39:51,540
In any case, he's very sincere.

522
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:55,610
That's good to hear.

523
00:39:59,460 --> 00:40:01,660
It's snowing.

524
00:40:46,810 --> 00:40:51,520
An unexpected mishap. An unexpected mishap.

525
00:41:04,620 --> 00:41:06,520
What are you thinking about?

526
00:41:06,520 --> 00:41:08,620
You are so focused.

527
00:41:09,450 --> 00:41:11,690
I'm thinking about what Teacher used to say.

528
00:41:11,690 --> 00:41:15,390
That the disciples from Kunlun Void love to brew peach blossom honey.

529
00:41:15,390 --> 00:41:16,950
That's only to humor the kids.

530
00:41:16,950 --> 00:41:18,530
It's too sweet.

531
00:41:18,530 --> 00:41:21,120
Are you interested?

532
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:22,850
Is it sweet?

533
00:41:22,850 --> 00:41:25,720
Then, please pack some for me.

534
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:28,970
Zhen Zhen has loved sweets ever since he was little.

535
00:41:28,970 --> 00:41:33,550
When he got sick, he would only drink his medicine if it was sweet.

536
00:41:34,070 --> 00:41:35,830
Zhen Zhen?

537
00:41:35,830 --> 00:41:38,910
When did you get married?

538
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:43,430
He's not my child. I'm talking about High God Bai Zhen.

539
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:48,770
You are right. Compared to you, High God Bai Zhen is still a kid.

540
00:41:48,770 --> 00:41:51,230
I'll pack some extra for you.

541
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:17,580
Are you cold?

542
00:42:17,580 --> 00:42:19,650
I'll close the windows.

543
00:42:19,650 --> 00:42:21,660
No need.

544
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:27,790
It's getting late.

545
00:42:27,790 --> 00:42:30,450
You should go back to rest.

546
00:42:31,170 --> 00:42:32,600
It's my fault.

547
00:42:32,600 --> 00:42:35,240
I forgot you still have to recuperate.

548
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:37,610
I'll be leaving now.

549
00:43:17,030 --> 00:43:22,990
”Cold” by Aska Yang & Diamond Zhang

550
00:43:22,990 --> 00:43:25,010
♫ The temperature gradually drops as night falls ♫

551
00:43:25,010 --> 00:43:27,640
♫ Fallen blossoms become frost ♫

552
00:43:27,640 --> 00:43:32,910
♫ In the distance, you are gazing out afar and exhausting the twilight hours ♫

553
00:43:32,910 --> 00:43:42,160
♫ Without considering the difficulty of forgetting each other ♫

554
00:43:44,250 --> 00:43:46,310
♫ Tender peach blossoms are cold ♫

555
00:43:46,310 --> 00:43:51,580
♫ How could you bear to let go of so many uncertain hearts in the previous lifetime ♫

556
00:43:51,580 --> 00:43:58,970
♫ And still show no pain, no yearning, and no signs that you were forced? ♫

557
00:43:58,970 --> 00:44:03,990
♫ All are just illusions ♫

558
00:44:05,050 --> 00:44:10,680
♫ During the cold night, my yearning for you runs as a river ♫

559
00:44:10,680 --> 00:44:15,840
♫ And transforming into spring soil to nourish me ♫

560
00:44:15,840 --> 00:44:20,360
♫ The fleeting years fill up my lover’s sleeve ♫

561
00:44:20,360 --> 00:44:26,450
♫ Pieces of flowers and plants flow into the waters ♫

562
00:44:26,450 --> 00:44:32,010
♫ The cold will of heaven dresses in glittering colors of flowers ♫

563
00:44:32,010 --> 00:44:37,050
♫ And fall into the mortal realm to hurt my feelings ♫

564
00:44:37,050 --> 00:44:39,850
♫ Calamities are easy to overcome, but trials of love are difficult to overcome ♫

565
00:44:39,850 --> 00:44:48,870
♫ My depreciating heart still holds some hatred from
my previous life ♫

566
00:44:55,860 --> 00:45:01,090
♫ The cold three lives and three worlds are as sudden
as a dream ♫

567
00:45:01,090 --> 00:45:06,660
♫ The wind dries my tears in those instantaneous years ♫

568
00:45:06,660 --> 00:45:10,910
♫ If we can no longer recognize our memories ♫

569
00:45:10,910 --> 00:45:17,230
♫ Then allow our love to rest deep within the dust ♫

570
00:45:17,230 --> 00:45:22,490
♫ When will the cold ten miles of peach blossoms
bloom again? ♫

571
00:45:22,490 --> 00:45:27,770
♫ I see a gust of wind under the tree again ♫

572
00:45:27,770 --> 00:45:30,620
♫ Fallen blossoms are of love, flowing waters are of heartlessness ♫

573
00:45:30,620 --> 00:45:39,530
♫ Don’t allow our past grudges, love, and hate to chill the innocence of the flower ♫

574
00:45:41,310 --> 00:45:52,080
♫ My hope in this lifetime is to be with you ♫
